---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Editorial" description="Daily news scan + weekly synthesis on agent platform systems.">
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 tracking-tight">Editorial</h1>
  <p class="text-lg mb-8 max-w-2xl" style="color: var(--color-ink-dim);">
    Daily news scan weekdays; weekly long-form synthesis Fridays. All content
    is primary-source-first and linked back to raw material.
  </p>

  <p style="color: var(--color-ink-dim);">
    First three seed deep-dives publish during Week 2 of launch:
  </p>
  <ul class="mt-4 space-y-3 max-w-2xl">
    <li>
      <strong>The five agent harnesses worth tracking in 2026</strong> — Claude Code, Codex CLI, Aider, OpenDevin, Cline
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Memory is the next harness moat</strong> — why Letta, mem0, MemGPT, and Claude memory don't yet behave alike
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Context repositories: the pattern emerging under every serious agent team</strong>
      — a worked case study from the Synaplex workspace's own tooling
    </li>
  </ul>
</Layout>
